#Text=Wikinews interviews Chilean Paralympic skier Jorge Migueles
#Text=Wednesday , December 19 , 2012
#Text=Wikinews reporter LauraHale interviews Chilean Paralympic skier Jorge Migueles
#Text=Recently , Wikinews spent time with with Chilean Paralympic skier Jorge Migueles who was in Copper Mountain , Colorado for the IPC Nor-Am Cup .
#Text=I 'm interviewing Jorge Migueles , he is here from Chile .
#Text=And you 're from Santiago .
#Text=Yes , from Santiago .
#Text=What you 're what classification ?
#Text=LW4 , I have a prosthetic I ski with , special for skiing , I have an amputation below the knee .
#Text=When people think of skiing , they do n't automatically think Chile as a great place for skiers , and developing skiers .
#Text=How did the skier [ Jorge Migueles ] from Chile become a skier ?
#Text=Yes it is a good place because all the big teams — USA , Austria , Canada — go for training there and they go [ ... ]
#Text=in September because the snow is very hard for training , very icy , and it is very close to Santiago , to the airport , it is more easy for the logistics for the team .
#Text=I take it that you really like skiing ?
#Text=Yeah .
#Text=Do you do any other sports ?
#Text=Yes , I competed in triathlon , but only for a hobby .
#Text=I got training in Santiago before to come here , to ski[ ? ] here and one , two months in Europe .
#Text=So the triathlon helps you with your skiing ?
#Text=Yeah .
#Text=I take it your taking to go to Sochi ?
#Text=Yeah , I try .
#Text=Has your country [ Chile ] won any Paralympic medals in the winter games ?
#Text=No , never , neither[ ? ] olympic nor paralympic .
#Text=So you want to be the first winter Paralympian medal from your country ?
#Text=I try that .
#Text=Very difficult .
#Text=Do you get government support for the winter Paralympic side ?

#Text=Not yet , but I try and get support from the government because in Chile all the sport in the summer in Santiago 2014 is all the sport in the summer is all they reimburse[ ? ] , the monies go there , in the winter it 's more difficult .
#Text=But I try that .
#Text=Is winter sport popular in Chile ?
#Text=Yeah , it 's popular , but it 's very expensive to practice skiing or snowboard .
#Text=The only other major news story that people know about in Chile is the earthquake , that did n't impact you that much you at all ?
#Text=Yes , a lot , because when [ ... ] had to stay here in United States training , and seeing in the news the earthquake , was very hard .
#Text=And your family and everything was okay , with that ?
#Text=Yes , they 're okay .
#Text=Is there anything people who know nothing about Paralympic sport in Chile should know ?
#Text=In London , in the past Olympic Game , one person with disability [ ... ] , he won gold medal in London . [ ... ]
#Text=He was the first Paralympic to win a medal in the history of Chile .
#Text=And now the people know this movement [ The Paralympics ] .
#Text=That 's very cool .
#Text=Okay .
#Text=Thank you very , very much .
#Text=Thank you .
#Text=Jorge Migueles at Solitude Station on Copper Mountain
